snippet.textDisplay:
Rexy: Blue, I say it’s time that we annihilate this virus once and for all! Am I right?!

Blue: Yes! And save our beloveds once and for all too, Rexy! We’re all in this together!

Rexy: Can We Do It?

Blue: Yes We Can!

Both: Let’s Do This!
